('Add company names to reservations', 'Add in company names for those with corporate rates.'),
('Block arrivals (night audit)', 'Block all arrivals still due to check in before processing the One Button. *Your terminal will be down temporarily, so if you check anyone in to a room, be sure to make a copy or imprint of the guest credit card. Do not forget to check the guest into the PMS once the system is up.'),
