('Update Marsha Interface Status', 'Update Marsha Interface Status. (F8-Rsrv-M-D . Make sure that MARSHA interface is running properly. You can tell by the cursor moving automatically through the sections. If it seems to be frozen or not responding properly, call PMS Support at 240-632-6000 Option 1-2-2 and ask for help. When done checking, hit “E” to get out of this screen.'),
